  16 Feb 2012; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> mozart-1.4.0-r2.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #396885

  02 Dec 2010; <keri@gentoo.org> mozart-1.4.0-r2.ebuild:
  Respect CFLAGS in dss

